#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In most newsgroups, attachments are prohibited: do not send unsolicited "
"attachments; if you are asked to send them, look who is asking for them &mdash; "
"normally, the person will want you to send them by email."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
